Description: A modern Activator replacement for rootless and rootful jailbreaks. Bind triggers like Touch ID, Power/Volume buttons, and Status Bar gestures to system actions, Siri automation, and custom TCP commands. Includes native arm64e support for iOS 14. https://github.com/saihgupr/RemoteCompanion
